        <item>
            <title>YAMAHA 发布电动电单车 MOTOROiD 2   加入 AI 技术实现自动驾驶目标</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/17/yamaha-motoroid2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=yamaha-motoroid2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/17/yamaha-motoroid2/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 07:42:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199525</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本品牌 YAMAHA 近日发表新自体平衡电单车「MOTOROiD2」，并在其中引入 AI 技术，在上一代电单车的基础上增强了人车互动的体验感受。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1199542 aligncenter" style="text-align: center;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.06-694x472.png" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.06-694x472.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.06-1280x871.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.06-768x522.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.06-1536x1045.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.06.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />（图片来源：<a href="https://global.yamaha-motor.com/showroom/event/japan-mobilityshow-2023/motoroid2/">global.yamaha-motor</a>）</p><p>MOTOROiD2 采用独特的后摇臂设计以保持自立平衡，而其更新增了一组可动轴关节，让车身后半部能够与前半部独立，朝向不同方向倾斜。</p><p>新车车身加强了流线造型设计，更取消了手把位置，换为在车头两侧增设扶手。另外，MOTOROiD2 采用纯电力推动，电池位于车身中央，摩打配置于后轴，外层有白色护罩搭配金色饰条。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.25-694x511.png" alt="" width="694" height="511" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.25-694x511.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.25-1223x900.png 1223w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.25-768x565.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.25-1536x1130.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.25.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.37-694x451.png" alt="" width="694" height="451" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.37-694x451.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.37-1280x832.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.37-768x499.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.37-1536x999.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.37.37.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.34-694x472.png" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.34-694x472.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.34-1280x870.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.34-768x522.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.34-1536x1044.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.34.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.41-694x503.png" alt="" width="694" height="503" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.41-694x503.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.41-1242x900.png 1242w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.41-768x557.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.41-1536x1113.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-15.00.41.png 1584w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199549" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-694x505.png" alt="" width="694" height="505" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-694x505.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-1236x900.png 1236w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-768x559.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1-1536x1119.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.38-1.png 1590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199550" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1-694x536.png" alt="" width="694" height="536" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1-694x536.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1-1166x900.png 1166w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1-768x593.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-14.59.47-1.png 1480w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（图片来源：<a href="https://global.yamaha-motor.com/showroom/event/japan-mobilityshow-2023/motoroid2/">global.yamaha-motor</a>）</p><p>而 YAMAHA 又开发了 AMCES 自动平衡制御系统，由人工智慧快速判断车身状态后不断小幅出力，以保持车身自立不倒，实现电单车自动驾驶的目标。再者，车辆亦配有 AI 脸部与手势辨识能力。</p><p>预计 YAMAHA 目前不会真正生产 MOTOROiD2 电动电单车，而该公司又指将在下个月于东京举行的 2023 年日本移动展上展示 Motoroid 2 原型。</p><div class="epyt-video-wr